CREATIVE DESIGNS GRP -L.L.C specializes in delivering Glass Reinforced Plastic (GRP) products and Glass Reinforced Cement (GRC), tailored to suit a wide range of industries and applications. We are proud to offer a diverse portfolio of premium products and designs, including but not limited to: 

•	Customized GRP sculptures & furniture; 
•	Customized GRC designs;
•	Wall Painting;
•	Maintenance works.

